{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 With notation as in Example 2.4, explain how any function {\i f}\u8196?\u8712?\u8196?({\i A}\u8196?\u8594?\u8196?{\i B}) determines a section of {\i \u960?}{\sub {\i A}}.\par}
