{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab \u8469?: the set of natural numbers (that is, nonnegative integers);\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab \u8484?: the set of integers;\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab \u8474?: the set of rational numbers;\par}
