{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Let us go through these sets one by one:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab \u8469?: (\u8469?,\u8198?\u8197?+\u8197?) is not a group (needs negative numbers, {\i x}\u8197?+\u8197?5\u8196?=\u8196?0 has no solution), and neither is (\u8469?,\u8198?\u8197?\u8901?\u8197?) (e.g., 5\u8197?\u8901?\u8197?{\i x}\u8196?=\u8196?1 has no solution in \u8469?).\par}
